The love of Sahaj Yogis is so overwhelming that I cant find words what to talk…

00:00:14.140 --> 00:00:30.400
You might be knowing that today in whole world the Sahaj Yogis are heading towards their evolution.

00:00:30.400 --> 00:00:46.940
Many Sahaj Yogis have reached a very high state, the source of joy flows in them.

00:00:46.940 --> 00:00:58.500
Some of them became subtle and are active in a special way.

00:00:58.500 --> 00:01:09.200
But in every country I see that they have their own style or conditionings… human being is everywhere same…

00:01:09.200 --> 00:01:20.280
and Sahaj Yoga is an innate state of being which has no relation from outside.

00:01:20.280 --> 00:01:38.720
Still, the ‘Attention’ which is a form of the nature, which we know as Kundalini…

00:01:38.720 --> 00:02:00.980
has the tape record of all the countries you have been through, all the births you have taken, the ways through which you passed and whatever states you have experienced…

00:02:00.980 --> 00:02:09.500
this is the reason I see that every country’s human being is little different.

00:02:09.500 --> 00:02:19.860
Its very surprising that human being catches so strongly to whatever is ‘illusion’….

00:02:19.860 --> 00:02:28.200
and to catch the truth how much he is arrogant. He is so lethargic…

00:02:28.200 --> 00:02:34.300
with such difficulty he accepts it… but very badly he keeps sticking to the untruth.

00:02:34.300 --> 00:02:40.420
That’s why it is so surprising for me.

00:02:40.420 --> 00:02:53.260
In the beginning I used to think that human being considers his name, village, position

00:02:53.260 --> 00:03:06.120
and all these degrees as important, but it is amazing to see that how deeply it affects.

00:03:06.120 --> 00:03:10.980
As soon as it all gets vanished….

00:03:10.980 --> 00:03:19.800
As soon as all this illusion gets erased… we make our attention lighter and lighter.

00:03:19.800 --> 00:03:25.620
In Sahaj Yoga this ‘ attention’ goes and unites with the God.

00:03:25.620 --> 00:03:31.760
This ‘attention’ gets dissolved in the omnipresent enlightened Param Chaitanya.

00:03:31.760 --> 00:03:38.920
This same human attention which we consider as form of nature,

00:03:38.920 --> 00:03:46.860
this flower which is the part of nature gets dipped in the ocean of Divine love!

00:03:46.860 --> 00:03:58.120
But sometimes it is amazing to see that this human attention is so heavy…so scattered…

00:03:58.120 --> 00:04:03.340
There is only one way to recognize sahaj yoga is that how much joy you are in,

00:04:03.340 --> 00:04:07.680
how much peace you are in, and how much love you are into…

00:04:07.680 --> 00:04:14.760
The people who are living in illusion cannot get Sahaj Yoga.

00:04:14.760 --> 00:04:19.020
What can be done through my hard work?

00:04:19.020 --> 00:04:26.980
Is that I can take your Kundalini on mine and leave you there but you always drop it…

00:04:26.980 --> 00:04:35.160
You cannot even enjoy where I take you to.

00:04:35.160 --> 00:04:42.060
In every country there are different type of problems.

00:04:42.060 --> 00:04:49.220
We must first understand what is the problem of our country, because first of all we should know our own problem.

00:04:49.220 --> 00:04:53.540
And what is the problem of other country also should be understood.

00:04:53.540 --> 00:05:01.540
Like, recently in U.K I have started my work, very slowly, I have taken very few people in my hands.

00:05:01.540 --> 00:05:09.660
I didn’t want to take many people, I thought first at least to establish twenty five people who should be established in Sahaj Yoga.

00:05:09.660 --> 00:05:15.600
You will be surprised to know that those people are very great souls!

00:05:15.600 --> 00:05:21.100
They have eternal faith in Sahaj Yoga, they understand that there is no other cure except Sahaj Yoga.

00:05:21.100 --> 00:05:29.400
After reaching the final stage, Sahaj Yoga is extremely ‘dynamic’ thing.

00:05:29.400 --> 00:05:39.240
And if there is any program of Sahaj Yoga, then there is nothing else greater and important for them.

00:05:39.240 --> 00:05:43.340
And for hours they will be involved in it….

00:05:43.340 --> 00:05:48.740
As if don’t know what is this thing which came from God which is to be given to this world….

00:05:48.740 --> 00:05:52.640
And the truth is that, ‘It Is’!! no doubt about it,

00:05:52.640 --> 00:06:03.520
but even after knowing this truth , I wont call it their fault

00:06:03.520 --> 00:06:11.800
but the reason for their shortcoming is that they did not get birth in Yoga Bhoomi (Land of Yoga) of India.

00:06:11.800 --> 00:06:18.200
Don’t know why God gave birth to such great people on that bhoga bhoomi (Land of Materialism)

00:06:18.200 --> 00:06:21.220
and you people have got birth on this Yoga Bhoomi.

00:06:21.220 --> 00:06:30.920
That bhoga bhoomi where they have no culture.

00:06:30.920 --> 00:06:37.800
They don’t even know if they have to wear sindoor (kumkum) on the forehead or on the nose.

00:06:37.800 --> 00:06:45.060
They don’t know the protocols of Puja, they don’t know the protocol of praying…

00:06:45.060 --> 00:06:52.920
they have no knowledge about God.

00:06:52.920 --> 00:06:56.700
They don’t know even how to sit on the ground.

00:06:56.700 --> 00:07:05.300
They don’t know anything, they don’t even know how to give claps while performing the ‘Aarti’.

00:07:05.300 --> 00:07:21.640
And such great souls… so innate they are… so loving…they love me so much… such respect they have towards me.. that I am surprised.

00:07:21.640 --> 00:07:27.280
Whenever they walk in front of me, in fact they don’t, but whenever they pass they bow and pass with their head bent down.

00:07:27.280 --> 00:07:32.800
They love me so much that anything in this whole world has no meaning for them in front of me.

00:07:32.800 --> 00:07:45.900
They have such deep feeling for me that they don’t know how should they respect me, in what way.

00:07:45.900 --> 00:07:51.920
I am surprised that how they have so much understanding of all this about me. But for themselves they are so much upset, they are behind themselves with a stick.

00:07:51.920 --> 00:07:55.720
I told them that, “ you can shoe beat yourself 108 times’

00:07:55.720 --> 00:08:00.220
but they do it thrice 108 times… wherever they get chance they start shoe beating themselves.

00:08:00.220 --> 00:08:06.560
They say that we want to scold ourselves. I did not hear from them anything else about others individually,

00:08:06.560 --> 00:08:09.860
no complaints about anyone, nothing, but only about themselves they think and speak,

00:08:09.860 --> 00:08:13.860
and for other person they say, “ He is such a nice person that I feel shame on myself in front of him”

00:08:13.860 --> 00:08:17.720
They don’t look at the other person in wrong way.

00:08:17.720 --> 00:08:20.540
They just look at themselves as wrong.

00:08:20.540 --> 00:08:26.600
You will be really surprised that all the time they are behind themselves with a stick.

00:08:26.600 --> 00:08:31.560
Here (in India) I see that all the vision is outside, just opposite.

00:08:31.560 --> 00:08:36.660
Such dedication they have that when I was coming, there were tears flowing from their eyes,

00:08:36.660 --> 00:08:41.940
I tried, but their tears didn’t stop.

00:08:41.940 --> 00:08:47.620
So much Sahaj and simple is their feeling…

00:08:47.620 --> 00:08:57.640
Till now I could only get around 21 people like them.

00:08:57.760 --> 00:09:05.520
But, they are deep, what we call as genuine..

00:09:05.520 --> 00:09:10.700
they themselves come and say that we are not genuine…

00:09:10.700 --> 00:09:16.640
as if somebody is coming and telling me that I am not genuine.

00:09:16.640 --> 00:09:22.840
“Mother, I have this fault, I have that mistake and untruthy within me…I am carrying untruth within me…”

00:09:22.840 --> 00:09:28.600
they say it with completely opened heart.

00:09:28.600 --> 00:09:38.040
And they don’t feel shy for it… to call themselves bad they don’t feel shy… but they don’t judge others.

00:09:38.040 --> 00:09:41.920
And they also tell me about the reasons why they are like this.

00:09:41.920 --> 00:09:48.120
They will come and say, “ I am like this because My Father was like this, this thing happened and so…psychologically it is like this so I am doing like this.”

00:09:48.120 --> 00:09:55.380
they tell the reason why they did something wrong, because it happened so at that time, that’s why I am doing like this.

00:09:55.380 --> 00:10:00.980
One or two people also come who have lot of badhas (negativities). They work hard and are quiet.

00:10:00.980 --> 00:10:11.220
They don’t speak anything but say that, “ please let all the untruth get out of me, may be something is still hiding within me” they are so much deep in silence within.

00:10:11.220 --> 00:10:19.060
But they have this problem that they don’t know how to do Puja, how to worship, poor people don’t even understand how to do it….

00:10:19.060 --> 00:10:24.500
I told them that I don’t even send any money to you still how you manage?

00:10:24.500 --> 00:10:29.080
Once I told them that I like this bread very much.

00:10:29.080 --> 00:10:34.040
So every time they came they brought same bread for me.

00:10:34.040 --> 00:10:37.960
I told them: “Who will eat so many breads?”

00:10:37.960 --> 00:10:43.300
I just said, but they don’t understand how to surrender, how to give.

00:10:43.300 --> 00:10:51.480
They are very well educated and intellectuals, they have read all your scriptures and literature.

00:10:51.480 --> 00:10:56.860
So its not difficult to make them understand Sahaj Yoga.

00:10:56.860 --> 00:11:01.300
They say that, Sahaj Yoga is the process of getting to subtle from gross state.

00:11:01.300 --> 00:11:04.600
They have written an introductory book about me.

00:11:04.600 --> 00:11:09.040
You wont believe it, they brought all the philosophers of the world and put them on Mother’s feet…

00:11:09.040 --> 00:11:16.400
They say, “They are nothing… these philosophers raised only questions, but Mother has answered all questions!!”

00:11:16.400 --> 00:11:24.320
They praise their fate and say that we are so fortunate to have Mother…

00:11:24.320 --> 00:11:32.780
One day Sahaj Yoga is going to reach a very great height and recognition.

00:11:32.780 --> 00:11:39.240
You are my foundations.

00:11:41.960 --> 00:11:45.980
Imagine how strong the foundation stones have to be.

00:11:45.980 --> 00:11:49.560
First thing bring in your attention“Are we genuine?”

00:11:49.560 --> 00:11:54.480
look at yourself, not on others… Look at yourself! Am I genuine?

00:11:54.480 --> 00:12:00.960
Look, they even don’t know how to pronounce the mantras, they cant even say “Shri Krishna”

00:12:00.960 --> 00:12:03.940
with lot of difficulty they are able to pronounce ‘Radha Krishna’.

00:12:03.940 --> 00:12:10.440
For you it is so easy… that you can cleanse your Vishuddhi. You just say ‘Radha Krishna’ and its cured…

00:12:10.440 --> 00:12:16.120
Now, they cant pronounce clearly ‘Radha Krishna’, so Shri Krishna gets little angry on it.

00:12:16.120 --> 00:12:24.060
Their pronunciation is also not all right, but, with you its easy and you can awaken him easily.

00:12:25.220 --> 00:12:30.360
They don’t know how to put kumkum. They don’t know what is kumkum for.

00:12:30.360 --> 00:12:38.320
They don’t know how to offer flowers, they don’t know how to make Shri Ganesha, they don’t know how to make swastika, every time they make it reverse.

00:12:38.320 --> 00:12:43.940
They never knew all these things.

00:12:43.940 --> 00:12:50.640
But even being so much surrendered and devoted, they are unable to achieve what you people have achieved.

00:12:50.640 --> 00:13:09.460
You have received a lot, but its value, still very few have understood deep within.

00:13:09.460 --> 00:13:16.060
Not that I have not given them Sahaj, not that I have not given them free of cost…

00:13:16.060 --> 00:13:23.080
I have given them same as you people have got from me.

00:13:23.080 --> 00:13:28.120
But, the Love they have for me is so unlimited.

00:13:28.120 --> 00:13:33.860
It seems that they have understood my relation with them since many births but you people have not yet been able to understand it.

00:13:33.860 --> 00:13:40.420
Why are you so limited to yourself?

00:13:41.600 --> 00:13:51.140
Being cells of same body, being part and parcel of same body, still you feel each other as separate and different.

00:13:51.140 --> 00:13:59.600
