00:14:15.480 --> 00:14:21.800
They made him all right in such a way that he left smoking.

00:14:21.800 --> 00:14:31.120
They corrected all his arguments, helped him in every way, as soon as they saw him smoking, they used to call him, sit with him.

00:14:31.120 --> 00:14:38.120
Went to their home and took all the packets out where ever they found and hid them.

00:14:38.120 --> 00:14:42.340
It wasn’t cigarette smoking, it was something else, what you call it…drug.

00:14:42.340 --> 00:14:46.040
