00:14:46.040 --> 00:14:51.200
And, that boy did not feel bad about it, he said that please you do something about it.

00:14:51.200 --> 00:15:05.740
That boy himself said and used to run to them and say “ please save me, that desire is approaching me, please save me, anyhow”.

00:15:05.740 --> 00:15:15.300
So much hard work they are doing to correct themselves.

00:15:18.280 --> 00:15:21.640
Here (in India) your society itself is corrected one!

00:15:21.640 --> 00:15:26.180
You don’t know in what heavenly land you are living in.

00:15:26.180 --> 00:15:30.220
there they don’t know about mother or sister…

00:15:30.220 --> 00:15:37.260
Such a filth and dirty is there… every house there is liquor… drinking…

00:15:37.260 --> 00:15:42.860
such bad relations they have… Nothing like family, don’t know about mother, don’t know about father.

00:15:42.860 --> 00:15:47.760
You ask someone what about your mother? He will say, “ don’t know, she has married someone else and gone”.

00:15:47.760 --> 00:15:53.480
Characterless… everyone with damaged Mooladhara.

00:15:53.480 --> 00:15:58.260
Even being born in such country they came with Shri Ganesha to me… “

00:15:58.260 --> 00:16:21.480
Mother please give us innocence” they broke the head in front of Shri Ganesha, catching ears…asking for forgiveness… and a bravery in it.

00:16:29.000 --> 00:16:39.720
They are so much aware of themselves and also about others. is truth.

00:16:39.720 --> 00:16:46.920
They told about so many miracles and experiences of Sahaj Yoga.

00:16:46.920 --> 00:16:51.360
You have got one letter which I sent.

00:16:51.360 --> 00:16:56.320
It was all of them who found that thing out about me.

00:16:56.340 --> 00:16:59.780
About me they found out the fact.

00:16:59.780 --> 00:17:13.400
Still, you people could not understand it and haven’t seen it, but they could.

00:17:13.400 --> 00:17:18.200
They understood that yes it is like this, this is it… to say it is Mahamaya but within us it

00:17:18.200 --> 00:17:22.620
They have not achieved what you have.

00:17:22.620 --> 00:17:32.060
But they have put everything for it, all their efforts, they have understood that the time of evolution has come and Sat Yuga is standing on the door.

00:17:32.060 --> 00:17:37.360
They know that if this door wont open then destruction could not be stopped.

00:17:37.360 --> 00:17:45.620
