00:17:45.620 --> 00:17:50.060
They are responsible for Sahaj Yoga. No one can dare to speak against Sahaj Yoga.

00:17:50.060 --> 00:17:58.840
They don’t speak against Sahaj among themselves, but if someone else speaks then they just take him to task and make him understand what it is.

00:17:58.840 --> 00:18:08.780
If I tell them that 24 hours you sit without food, they will…!!!

00:18:08.780 --> 00:18:12.780
But, it does not mean that you people are less than that.

00:18:12.780 --> 00:18:23.340
Some of you have achieved the heights and state, its extraordinary.

00:18:23.360 --> 00:18:34.920
But that feeling of achieving is the problem about self.

00:18:34.920 --> 00:18:41.360
There is a meaning in keeping the attention steady.

00:18:41.360 --> 00:18:45.040
It doesn’t mean that you look here or there.

00:18:45.040 --> 00:18:51.600
The attention is steady only when all the dirt over it gets cleansed.

00:18:51.600 --> 00:18:54.740
When it becomes light.

00:18:54.740 --> 00:18:57.980
There is a very big curse on our country (India).

00:18:57.980 --> 00:19:10.240
It’s a very deeply located within us and that I call as ‘Sin against the Father’.

00:19:10.240 --> 00:19:17.740
We have committed sin against our Father in heaven.

00:19:17.740 --> 00:19:21.300
What is it?

00:19:21.300 --> 00:19:24.160
It is all the time thinking that “we are poor, we have poverty.

00:19:24.160 --> 00:19:32.280
We don’t have money, how will it go like this…what about my stomach… all these beggar like thinking.

00:19:32.280 --> 00:19:38.440
How will we pull on with money, what will happen to my children?

00:19:38.440 --> 00:19:52.580
If you have faith in God then at least leave this to him that he will give you food, otherwise what is there to have faith in God

00:19:52.580 --> 00:20:00.220
that even he cannot give you food and look after your needs.

00:20:00.220 --> 00:20:05.000
This is very great sin we are doing.

00:20:05.000 --> 00:20:15.300
If we leave this food and all arrangements on God, then Indians can achieve very great height.

00:20:15.300 --> 00:20:24.000
There are two kinds of Sin. One is to doubt on the fatherhood of the father, and second I call as ‘Sin against the Mother’ that is there in West

00:20:24.000 --> 00:20:37.060
in which there is immorality, indulgences, materialism, comfort and to get totally free… out of control, this is the problem there.

00:20:37.060 --> 00:20:40.540
Both the ways lead you straight to hell.

00:20:40.540 --> 00:20:49.320
Doing anything for Money, whatever wrong you have to do to make money… its all right.

00:20:49.320 --> 00:20:52.660
This is the sin of Indians.

00:20:52.660 --> 00:20:57.320
I am not talking about government. I am talking about God about the kingdom of God.

00:20:57.320 --> 00:21:02.880
When you are in the Kingdom of God then, he will give if he desires or he will not if he doesnt…

00:21:02.880 --> 00:21:06.000
what’s the problem in at least having this attitude within?

00:21:06.000 --> 00:21:09.720
He will do if he will and he will not if he wont…

00:21:09.740 --> 00:21:17.000
“ As you keep me, I shall be” if a Sahaj yogi just has this feeling within that “ As you will keep me, I shall live!!!,

00:21:17.000 --> 00:21:22.740
let me see how you will keep me” you can just enjoy everything.

00:21:22.740 --> 00:21:31.080
You just start enjoying it… you say, “ let me see how you will keep me, you will keep me hungry?

00:21:31.080 --> 00:21:38.100
O.K let me see how many days you will keep me starving!!!” “As you will let me live, I shall live!!!

00:21:38.100 --> 00:21:44.520
You make me walk, I will…, make me sit on horse, I will…., you will get into this bliss and joy….!!!!!

00:21:44.520 --> 00:21:48.940
You people are lucky to have been born in this great country that rest everything is all right,

00:21:48.940 --> 00:21:56.300
your parents are all right, your wife and children are all right, you are moral… most of you.

00:21:56.300 --> 00:22:06.080
Some of you are… But not so bad… it can be corrected.

00:22:06.080 --> 00:22:10.940
There is so much sin, the other one, that everybody’s eyes just keep moving…like this…

00:22:10.940 --> 00:22:14.220
this… all the time, of every man and woman… its such a negativity in them.

00:22:14.220 --> 00:22:16.920
Transmitting the negativity to each other through eyes.

00:22:16.920 --> 00:22:21.780
One woman goes, she looks on men, then the men look on women, then other,… it just goes on there like this… I said what is this?

00:22:21.780 --> 00:22:25.280
they said, ‘ Mother what to do here everyone gets this negativity in eyes.. what to do?”

00:22:25.280 --> 00:22:30.400
I said, “keep your eyes to the ground.” How was Shri Lakshmana, he only used to see the feet of Shri Sita.

00:22:30.400 --> 00:22:39.760
Keep the eyes low. Gradually all these badhas will go away spontaneously. If you will not do all this then what will that negativity do living in you?

00:22:39.760 --> 00:22:47.300
That bhoot which is playing through you and doing all this and using you, will run away by itself.

00:22:47.300 --> 00:22:54.600
If you don’t move your eyes here and there then that bhoot will just run away from you.

00:22:54.600 --> 00:22:59.240
And, till you will keep moving your eyes, the bhoots will keep sitting there in you.

00:22:59.240 --> 00:23:06.780
They accepted it… and now when they walk on the street they walk with eyes like this on the mother earth… low… this is obedience…

00:23:06.780 --> 00:23:11.260
Mother said and it is accepted and agreed!!

00:23:11.260 --> 00:23:16.260
These are the sign of true children.

00:23:16.260 --> 00:23:20.840
It is for your benevolence, for your wellbeing.

00:23:20.840 --> 00:23:26.400
You must understand this, that whatever you have got in sahaj yoga, you have to achieve it in this life itself.

00:23:26.400 --> 00:23:31.600
I have to achieve it, not the other… I have to… not others,

00:23:31.600 --> 00:23:36.460
leave of others, don’t worry about others, look within,

00:23:36.460 --> 00:23:41.200
how much I have achieved the state till now, how profound and deep I have gone in sahaj yoga?

00:23:41.200 --> 00:23:46.640
How am I behaving with myself, why am I acting with myself? Why am I cheating myself?

00:23:46.640 --> 00:23:57.200
Why am I lying to myself? Why am I torturing myself? What have I got?

00:23:57.200 --> 00:24:01.460
Look….. all the treasure is opened for you… just come in….

00:24:01.460 --> 00:24:08.500
no matter how you are, just come in, get inside.. I will give you bath and make you sit cleansed.

00:24:08.500 --> 00:24:14.140
Then what to think? How deep have we got inside the cool wave of Ganga?

00:24:14.140 --> 00:24:18.340
It is just flowing completely… “take whatever you want…take it my child…”

00:24:18.340 --> 00:24:22.100
how much pitcher we have filled? Our attention is just scattered and running here and there…

00:24:22.100 --> 00:24:29.780
the moment you will have look within, you will understand that it is you who has cheated yourself,

00:24:29.780 --> 00:24:33.920
no one else. This is a very big gap. It is harmful for sahaj yoga.

00:24:33.920 --> 00:24:40.600
Not to keep attention toward self is the most harmful thing in Sahaj Yoga.

00:24:40.600 --> 00:24:45.540
And this introspection is only in that person’s nature who had been seeking since many lives….

00:24:45.540 --> 00:24:51.560
