00:24:56.640 --> 00:25:01.940
The one who has broken his head by striking against the walls in darkness knows and thinks…

00:25:01.940 --> 00:25:08.180
No, look towards the door…keep the attention towards the door.. to the way to the door.

00:25:08.180 --> 00:25:13.660
He doesn’t know anything else but knows and says…

00:25:13.660 --> 00:25:25.340
yes, I know, I have got it, the vibrations are flowing from within… My Sahasrara is pierced and I have known the truth!!!

